Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Central atrium exclusive to building tenants

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Encompassing a full city block bordered by SW 4th Avenue, SW 5th Avenue, SW Oak Street and SW Pine Street, Five Oak is located a block from US Bancorp Tower and a short walk from Pine Street Market, Pioneer Square, and numerous hotel, dining and shopping destinations. The building features an updated lobby, central atrium and gathering space for tenants, showers & lockers, secure bike parking and underground parking.
